{"4341650": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "The Night We Met", "steam_appid": 4341650, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "controller_support": "full", "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4341650/extras/5b4848b9b6c000c6ed5f23b1656aeab6.avif?t=1775740456\" width=1560 height=390 /></span>《The Night We Met》是一款成人視覺小說，您的選擇將決定故事的結局。在整個遊戲過程中，您將沉浸在一場萬聖節派對中，您可以與多位女孩調情，如果您運籌帷幄，甚至可以與她們共度美好時光。 遊戲已完整發布，共包含42個場景（31個NSFW和11個SFW），超過700張獨特渲染圖，以及7個不同結局和一個隱藏結局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4341650/extras/f9848670237b11ea2743ffeb7267855f.poster.avif?t=1775740456\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4341650/extras/f9848670237b11ea2743ffeb7267855f.webm?t=1775740456\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4341650/extras/f9848670237b11ea2743ffeb7267855f.mp4?t=1775740456\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>角色介紹</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4341650/extras/7e81c536ecb9d80e0d4069ee9b1bfeea.avif?t=1775740456\" width=600 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Alex是主角，一位剛剛與Eliza分手的年輕人，因為他發現了她的背叛。今晚的派對上，他希望能遇到一位認真的女孩，幫助他忘記過去。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4341650/extras/eefef6f06b65ab7bc60d1b3b20c66a37.avif?t=1775740456\" width=600 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Anna是一位年輕的心理學本科生，已經單身幾個月了，感到需要重新融入社交生活。她非常善於傾聽，但同時也極具競爭意識和進取心。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4341650/extras/fd44b68743060bb6683bd145e3ce119b.avif?t=1775740456\" width=600 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sierra是一個非常害羞的女孩，夢想在某次派對上找到她的白馬王子。她喜歡恐怖電影、搖滾音樂以及一切另類的事物。她通常平靜溫柔，但如果有人觸碰她的底線，她絕不會手軟。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4341650/extras/a9e3afe7a9061626908cb090b51122ed.avif?t=1775740456\" width=600 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Eliza是Elizabeth的暱稱，她美麗、金髮、外向。她也是Alex熱情奔放的前女友。他們分手才短短兩週，但今晚，Eliza已經制定了一個計劃，試圖與他實現她的一個性幻想。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4341650/extras/a174468ff4567ed71145f29df19ffedf.avif?t=1775740456\" width=600 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ian是典型的視覺小說男主角：高大、肌肉發達、英俊，有著完美髮型和藍色眼睛。所有女孩都為他著迷，所有男孩都希望成為他。但這一次，你不是他。與這個善於操控的花花公子一較高下，阻止他贏得你喜歡的女孩！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4341650/extras/9b788b155afd4618a92fa9c6f0b81255.avif?t=1775740456\" width=600 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Emma是房子的主人，也是所有參與者之間的紐帶。她組織這次活動只有一個原因：盡情享受性愛！作為一個真正的色情狂，她會不惜一切贏得Alex的心（和他的身體）。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4341650/extras/2028e5668a65e63c2c9a88c9d90302a1.poster.avif?t=1775740456\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4341650/extras/2028e5668a65e63c2c9a88c9d90302a1.webm?t=1775740456\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4341650/extras/2028e5668a65e63c2c9a88c9d90302a1.mp4?t=1775740456\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>劇情</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >透過Alex、Anna和Sierra的視角，體驗一場難忘的萬聖節派對。沉浸在一個分為四個獨立章節的故事中，在那裡您將了解角色、與他們調情，並參與有史以來最精彩的真心話大冒險遊戲。 您的選擇真的很重要，可以改變故事的走向：有時微妙，有時明顯。探索8個獨特的結局，實現與女孩們共度美好時光的夢想，體驗所有行為的後果！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4341650/extras/598822eaf9e9d94bfc61176aa0da7bf4.poster.avif?t=1775740456\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4341650/extras/598822eaf9e9d94bfc61176aa0da7bf4.webm?t=1775740456\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4341650/extras/598822eaf9e9d94bfc61176aa0da7bf4.mp4?t=1775740456\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>內容標籤</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >口交</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >深喉</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >陰道性交</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >肛交</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >女性主導</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >激烈性愛</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >打屁股</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >出軌</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >挑逗</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >墮落</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >NTR（可迴避）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >NTS（可迴避）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >綠帽（可迴避）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Trap/偽娘（可迴避）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >顏射</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >內射</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >暴露癖</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自慰</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"