0/extras/2028e5668a65e63c2c9a88c9d90302a1.webm?t=1775740456\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4341650/extras/2028e5668a65e63c2c9a88c9d90302a1.mp4?t=1775740456\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>劇情</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >透過Alex、Anna和Sierra的視角，體驗一場難忘的萬聖節派對。沉浸在一個分為四個獨立章節的故事中，在那裡您將了解角色、與他們調情，並參與有史以來最精彩的真心話大冒險遊戲。 您的選擇真的很重要，可以改變故事的走向：有時微妙，有時明顯。探索8個獨特的結局，實現與女孩們共度美好時光的夢想，體驗所有行為的後果！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4341650/extras/598822eaf9e9d94bfc61176aa0da7bf4.poster.avif?t=1775740456\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4341650/extras/598822eaf9e9d94bfc61176aa0da7bf4.webm?t=1775740456\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4341650/extras/598822eaf9e9d94bfc61176aa0da7bf4.mp4?t=1775740456\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>內容標籤</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >口交</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >深喉</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >陰道性交</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >肛交</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >女性主導</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >激烈性愛</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >打屁股</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >出軌</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >挑逗</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >墮落</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >NTR（可迴避）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >NTS（可迴避）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >綠帽（可迴避）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Trap/偽娘（可迴避）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >顏射</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >內射</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragr